CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776708666
OL,3,CEnergy plant emerges as key part of
OL,4,Csecret government plans for UK food
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FAn energy plant on Teesside has
OL,8,Femerged as a key part of secret
OL,9,Fcontingency plans drawn up by the
OL,10,Fgovernment in the event of potential
OL,11,Ffood shortages due to the war in Iran.
OL,13,FEnsus, at Wilton near Redcar, is now
OL,14,Fback up and running producing carbon
OL,15,Fdioxide (CO2) thanks to a government
OL,16,Ffunding package, after production was
OL,17,Fhalted in September 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
