FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776708666
OL,3,CEnergy plant emerges as key part of
OL,4,Csecret government plans for UK food
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FThe contingency plan, drawn up by
OL,8,Fministers for a "worst case scenario"
OL,9,Fand leaked to The Times on Thursday
OL,10,F(16 April), reportedly suggests CO2
OL,11,Fimports could be hit if the Iran
OL,12,Fconflict continues into the summer
OL,13,Fwithout a resolution.
OL,15,FThe gas has a range of important uses,
OL,16,Fincluding playing a vital role in food
OL,17,Fstorage and transportation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776708666
OL,3,CEnergy plant emerges as key part of
OL,4,Csecret government plans for UK food
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FITV News Tyne Tees understands the
OL,8,FEnsus plant would be relied upon to
OL,9,Fboost supplies of CO2 in the UK if
OL,10,Fthat 'worst case scenario' were to
OL,11,Fhappen.
OL,13,FThe chairman of Ensus, Grant Pearson,
OL,14,Ftold ITV News Tyne Tees it is right
OL,15,Fthat the UK increases its own
OL,16,Fproduction of vital chemicals, rather
OL,17,Fthan becoming too reliant on imports.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776708666
OL,3,CEnergy plant emerges as key part of
OL,4,Csecret government plans for UK food
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FHe said: "Right across the chemical
OL,8,Fsector in particular, we're seeing
OL,9,Fclosures of plants, which not only
OL,10,Fimpact the jobs in those sectors, but
OL,11,Fmeans we're not making those basic raw
OL,12,Fmaterials.
OL,14,F"Hopefully this is a bit of a wake-up
OL,15,Fcall for the country to think again
OL,16,Fabout how we should be addressing some
OL,17,Fof these challenges."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
