PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776708666
OL,3,CEnergy plant emerges as key part of
OL,4,Csecret government plans for UK food
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FSpeaking on Thursday morning following
OL,8,Fthe leak, Business Secretary Peter
OL,9,FKyle said the public should be
OL,10,F"reassured" that ministers are making
OL,11,Fcontingency plans for the impact of
OL,12,Fthe Iran war.
OL,14,FMr Kyle told Times Radio the
OL,15,FGovernment did not comment on leaks,
OL,16,Fbut added: "It is difficult for me,
OL,17,Fbecause, of course, these leaks are
OL,18,Fvery unhelpful.
OL,26,@xD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
