FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776708666
OL,3,CEnergy plant emerges as key part of
OL,4,Csecret government plans for UK food
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,F"But when people do read it, they need
OL,8,Fto be reassured that we are doing this
OL,9,Fkind of planning, and we are doing
OL,10,Fthis kind of scenario planning."
OL,12,FMr Kyle said he had mothballed a CO2-
OL,13,Fproducing plant in Teesside shortly
OL,14,Fafter becoming Business Secretary in
OL,15,Forder to prevent it shutting down
OL,16,Fcompletely.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
